  "pageTitle": "配備數位座艙的資源回收中心",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page case-study-detail-page case-study-detail-page-ai\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"case-detail-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">智慧回收箱 詳情</p>\n        <h1 id=\"case-detail-title\">配備數位座艙的資源回收中心</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">資源回收中心的參考資料，結合分揀模組、稱重、報告及遠端操作可視性。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-section case-detail-timeline-section\" id=\"smart-recovery-center\" aria-labelledby=\"smart-recovery-center-timeline-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">參考時間軸</p>\n          <h2 id=\"smart-recovery-center-timeline-title\">從混合接收到數位營運可視化</h2>\n          <p>案例依買方評估流程排序：背景、合作單位、限制、解決方案，以及前後比較。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"case-detail-timeline\" aria-label=\"案例 詳情 時間軸\">\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>01</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">專案背景</p>\n              <h3>混合回收物流需要資料支援路由</h3>\n              <p>該中心結合了收件、物料分組、分類、稱重、儲存及出廠物流，涵蓋混合可回收與市政廢棄物流。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>工作流程區域</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">6 區域</strong><span>接收到外發</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>物料範圍</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 串流</strong><span>可回收物與市政廢棄物</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>02</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">合作單位</p>\n              <h3>匿名市級回收服務提供商</h3>\n              <p>合作單位需要對進料物料、已分選的產出、每日 的運作狀態及管理審查報告有更好的可視性。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>管理層</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 駕駛艙</strong><span>中央操作顯示</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>審查模式</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">每日</strong><span>輸出與狀態報告</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>03</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">實際限制</p>\n              <h3>物理流程與資料流量必須保持同步</h3>\n              <p>該專案必須將分揀模組、稱重點、駕駛艙顯示、儲存區及遠端管理連接起來，且不將作業與報告分離。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>資料點</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">3 群組</strong><span>輸入 / 輸出 / 狀態</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>遠端需求</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 介面</strong><span>管理能見度</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>04</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">解法</p>\n              <h3>分揀模組加上稱重與數位駕駛艙</h3>\n              <p>參考套件涵蓋分揀模組、智慧稱重點、駕駛艙顯示、遠端管理介面，以及報告 支援的吞吐量與類別。</p>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>系統區塊</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">4 區塊</strong><span>分類/稱重/報告/管理</span></dd></div>\n                <div><dt>輸出視圖</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">1 儀表板</strong><span>駕駛艙摘要</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"case-detail-timeline-item\">\n            <div class=\"case-detail-timeline-marker\"><span>05</span></div>\n            <div class=\"case-detail-stage-card\">\n              <p class=\"case-detail-stage-label\">前後對比</p>\n              <h3>操作能見度成為案件證據之一</h3>\n              <div class=\"case-detail-comparison\">\n                <div><span>之前</span><strong>分離的物料流與報告</strong><p>經理對接收、分類和儲存日常的連結了解有限。</p></div>\n                <div><span>之後</span><strong>從接收到報告的可見路徑</strong><p>參考影片和駕駛艙截圖展示了物料路線、分選產出和報告工作流程。</p></div>\n              </div>\n              <dl class=\"case-detail-metrics\">\n                <div><dt>證據集</dt><dd><strong class=\"case-detail-metric-value\">2 資產</strong><span>影片與駕駛艙截圖</span></dd></div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section case-detail-action-section ai-rfq-section\" aria-label=\"案例操作\">\n        <div class=\"rfq-action-strip case-detail-action-strip\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求參考包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">返回案例研究</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
